rComments: "This class will determine who the winners are...and who the losers are"-Professor Jiaxin Gong

I heart Gong!! I spend the whole class making fun of his sayings. Funniest quote ever: "I have to go to the bathroom for a while." Come on, who says that?? If you really want to learn anything about accounting, don't take his section.

He is new to America and has some crazy quotes.  Half the time you are trying to decipher what he is saying.  He is a very nice guy with good attitude towards accounting, but will not help you at all in the future.  Look out for the massive belt that he wears.
